# Vue.js Task Management Application

## Overview

This project is a simple task management application built using Vue.js and Vuetify. It allows users to create, update, and delete tasks using a form. The submitted tasks are displayed on the right side of the interface. 

## Features

- **Dynamic Task Form**: Users can fill out a form with all required fields (title, description, etc.) to create a new task.
- **Task Display**: Once submitted, the tasks are displayed on the right side of the page.
- **Update and Delete Tasks**: Users can update existing tasks or delete them as needed.
- **Static Data**: The application uses static data for demonstration purposes and does not connect to any backend or database.

